        <h4>Some hiring managers hate bootcamps</h4>
        <p>To that last point, be warned that there are people in hiring positions who have stopped hiring recent bootcamp grads altogether.</p>
{% endslide %}
{% slide %}
        <blockquote>
            <p>{% ext "https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=22301802" %}"Of 20 people I've interviewed who completed a coding bootcamp without prior CS education in the past year or so, I think 1 passed the phone screen. At this point I outright reject them because of the futility."{% endext %}</p>
        </blockquote>
{% endslide %}
