            <p>{% ext "https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=31695850#:~:text=For%20everyone%20reading,the%20underlying%20concepts." %}"For everyone reading, being on the hiring side I would advise against bootcamps. We pretty much stopped recruiting from those because the signal to noise ratio was just too low. It seems a lot of bootcamps teach with rote, rather than by looking at the underlying concepts."{% endext %}</p>
