        </blockquote>
{% endslide %}
{% slide %}
        <p>Keep in mind, this is a sampling of some comments from discussions on Hacker News, but bootcamps may try to sell you on the idea that they are producing graduates that are seen as somehow "elite". Not everyone shares this view.</p>
        <p>If you think a coding bootcamp might be for you, go into it with clear eyes. Understand that <span data-annotate>not all bootcamps are created equal</span>, that you'll need to <span data-annotate>verify their claims</span> for yourself, and that successfully completing one is <span data-annotate>not a golden ticket.</span></p>
